The kids can, uh, go on a couple of rides
while we ask where Zoo Gardens is.

00:52.167 --> 00:55.633
- I don't know.   - What could happen?
It's an amusement park.

00:56.067 --> 01:00.067
Stay off the guillotine ride.
Sharp turns.

01:00.067 --> 01:03.167
Get out while you still can!

01:03.167 --> 01:05.333
Lizzy, I'm lost!

01:05.800 --> 01:08.567
- Hello?
- [ Cackling ]

01:09.000 --> 01:11.100
[ Screaming ]

01:11.100 --> 01:14.533
- Get me out of here!
- [ Gasps ]

01:14.533 --> 01:17.600
"No exit.
No one leaves Horrorland alive"?

01:17.600 --> 01:20.267
[ Mom Whimpering, Gasps ]

01:23.600 --> 01:25.433
[ Creature ]
We want you to stay.

01:27.867 --> 01:29.033
Now, you-- you listen to me.

01:29.033 --> 01:31.400
Now, we have a right to
leave whenever we want.

01:31.400 --> 01:35.200
Now you take off that stupid
mask and talk to me man-to-man.

01:35.200 --> 01:38.500
- [ Straining ]
- [ Growling ]

01:38.500 --> 01:40.967
It's, uh, not a mask.

01:40.967 --> 01:42.600
- [ Growling ]
- [ Mom ] Oh!

01:42.600 --> 01:45.600
- [ Family Screaming ]
- Let's get them!

01:45.600 --> 01:47.833
- [ Mom ] Oh, they're behind us!
- [ Luke ] Monsters!

01:48.267 --> 01:51.400
- There they are!
- [ Lizzy Screaming ]

01:51.400 --> 01:54.033
- [ Dad ] Help! No, run there!
- [ Snarling, Growling Continues ]

01:54.500 --> 01:57.433
- Get them!
- [ Dad ] This way!

01:57.433 --> 02:00.067
Come on! Hurry up!
Let's go! Let's go!

02:00.067 --> 02:02.400
[ Chuckling, Growling ]

02:04.400 --> 02:07.167
Who's there?
I said, who's there?

02:07.600 --> 02:09.000
- [ Fanfare ]
- [ Laughs ]

02:09.400 --> 02:11.900
Let's hear it for the
Morris family, everybody!

02:12.367 --> 02:16.833
- [ Hooting, Cheering ]
- Let's put 'em together for the Morrises!

02:17.700 --> 02:21.533
[ Laughs ] Ah, come on down, folks.
Watch your step! [ Laughs ]

02:21.533 --> 02:24.800
The Morrises!
[ Laughs ]

02:24.800 --> 02:27.300
- [ Applause Fades ]
- What is this?

02:27.800 --> 02:29.700
[ Laughing ]

02:30.100 --> 02:31.867
- Isn't she terrific?
- [ Hooting ]

02:32.367 --> 02:33.367
What do you want from us?

02:33.367 --> 02:36.833
What do we want from you?
We want to say thank you.

02:36.833 --> 02:39.400
Just a minute.
What do you mean, "thank you"?

02:39.400 --> 02:44.333
We wanna thank you for
being our guests today on--

02:44.333 --> 02:49.967
- [ Fanfare ]
- [ With Audience ] Horrorland Hidden Camera!

02:49.967 --> 02:52.100
That's right--
Horrorland Hidden Camera,

02:52.600 --> 02:55.267
the Monster Channel's
favorite television program.

02:55.267 --> 02:57.567
The Monster Channel?

02:57.967 --> 03:01.500
- Just stay calm.
- Oh, and we know how well you do that.

03:01.500 --> 03:05.000
- [ Laughing ]
- Here are some clips of the Morris family...

03:05.000 --> 03:07.000
"staying calm."

03:07.000 --> 03:11.067
Let's watch them in super slo-mo.

03:11.067 --> 03:15.467
- [ Organ: Up-temp, Bouncy ]
- [ Audience Laughing, Cheering ]

03:20.467 --> 03:23.533
[ Laughing, Cheering Continues ]

03:28.200 --> 03:31.933
[ Laughs ] Put your claws together
for the Morrises, folks, huh?

03:31.933 --> 03:35.600
They're good sports. Yeah!
[ Laughs ]

03:36.100 --> 03:38.167
Whoa! They love you guys.
[ Laughs ]

03:38.167 --> 03:41.433
- [ Drumroll, Exit Music ]
- Well, that's all the time we have for today.

03:41.867 --> 03:44.600
So, for all of us here
at Horrorland Hidden Camera,

03:45.033 --> 03:47.133
Bye-bye!

03:47.133 --> 03:50.067
- [ Ends ]
- [ Director ] That's a wrap.

03:50.067 --> 03:53.533
Hey, you guys were terrific. Listen,
we have another show coming up--

03:53.533 --> 03:57.000
a game show--
and you're gonna be the contestants.

03:57.000 --> 03:59.700
- We just wanna go home.
- Yeah.

04:00.133 --> 04:02.433
- You can't go home.
- What do you mean, we can't go home?

04:02.433 --> 04:06.567
You can't go home. Because if you do,
you won't get that new car!

04:06.567 --> 04:09.400
What new car? Who said
anything about a new car?

04:09.833 --> 04:11.433
It's the grand prize...
on the game show.

04:11.933 --> 04:15.067
- I don't get it.
- I understand. You're confused.

04:15.567 --> 04:17.300
First you find out
monsters really do exist,

04:17.800 --> 04:20.600
and then you find out
we have our own cable channel.

04:20.600 --> 04:22.000
It's a shock.

04:22.000 --> 04:25.833
Well, I guess we'll just have to
give that car to some other family.

04:25.833 --> 04:27.767
No, no, no.
No, wait. Just, uh--

04:27.767 --> 04:30.433
I don't think it would hurt
to just play the game.

04:30.433 --> 04:32.867
- Mmm.
- What kind of a car is it?

04:32.867 --> 04:37.467
- A brand-new sports utility vehicle.
- Dad--

04:37.467 --> 04:39.967
- Shh-shh-shh.
- We all sure could have loads of fun...

04:39.967 --> 04:42.400
- with a brand-new sports utility vehicle.
- Yeah.

04:42.400 --> 04:43.833
Good!
That's what I thought.

04:44.333 --> 04:45.833
- Oh, Sludge.
- Yeah, Retch?

04:45.833 --> 04:49.733
- Show the Morrises to makeup, will you?
- Uh-huh. Walk this way.

04:51.733 --> 04:54.167
Oop! Pardon me.

04:54.167 --> 04:56.500
# La-da, dee-dee, la-- #
Huh?

04:57.433 --> 04:59.333
[ Gasps ]
Oh!

04:59.767 --> 05:01.367
