- Well, Retch, I'm--

07:18.667 --> 07:21.633
Fabulous. And, Peggy, are you
excited to be here on Raw Deal?

07:21.633 --> 07:23.267
[ Mouthing Words ]

07:23.267 --> 07:25.267
- We are, Retch.
- Yes. Yes, we really are.

07:25.700 --> 07:27.000
He-He-Hey, so am I.
[ Chuckles ]

07:27.433 --> 07:30.667
Okay, let's play the game.
Holly?

07:31.100 --> 07:33.233
