07:41.200 --> 07:44.633
- Now, if the letter guessed appears on
our puzzle board back here--   - Wow!

07:44.633 --> 07:46.967
you will win the amount of
money on the card you picked

07:46.967 --> 07:49.333
and a chance to solve the puzzle.

07:49.333 --> 07:54.200
