- Doesn't matter. Nobody does.

07:54.200 --> 07:58.400
Now, today's puzzle is a phrase, and
the Morris parents will go first.

07:58.400 --> 08:01.267
- Come on down, gang.
- [ Applause ]

08:01.267 --> 08:05.900
