- [ Cheering, Whistling ]

08:18.967 --> 08:20.733
- Oh!
- [ Dad ] $200. That's really great.

08:21.167 --> 08:25.667
All right, Morrises.
Go ahead now and guess a letter.

08:27.167 --> 08:28.900
