09:14.800 --> 09:17.233
Anyone care to take a guess
and solve the puzzle...

09:17.233 --> 09:20.833
to win that fabulous
sport utility vehicle?

09:21.267 --> 09:23.233
- We'll take a "P."
- No "P."

09:23.233 --> 09:25.133
- Oh, there are no "P's."
